Happy Mother’s Day
Today, we celebrate the incredible women who give so much of themselves—our beloved customers and the amazing mothers who are part of our City Kia team.

Thank you for your trust, your dedication, and for being the foundation of your families and the heartbeat of our community.

You inspire us every day with your strength, love, and resilience.
From all of us at City Kia, we honor you today and always.

Happy Mother’s Day — and thank you for everything you do.
